to run the code you need to install python 3.7 and selenium
make sure that pip is installed in your terminal(cmd for windows)
to install selenium go to terminal and run: pip install selenium
to run the code go to the code directory path and type the command below:
python auto_buy_bot.py
This script will be running infinitely 

************************************************************************
To stop the script please type CTRL+C ON THE TERMINAL **ONLY ONE TIME**
************************************************************************

Note that you need a good internet connection for the bot to be running in a stable condition.

